---
description: Keep justfile aligned with scripts/*
globs: justfile,scripts/*.sh
alwaysApply: true
---

# Justfile / Scripts Alignment

- Every `scripts/*.sh` must have a corresponding justfile recipe (except `default`).
- Every recipe must delegate to a script.
- When scripts are added/renamed/removed, update the justfile.
- Recipe comments should match the script's header description.
